# Credit Card Fraud Detection

## Project Overview
Machine Learning based fraud detection system using Random Forest.

## Dataset
European credit card transactions dataset.

## Features
- EDA
- SMOTE Balancing
- Random Forest
- Fraud Analytics Dashboard
- Live Prediction

## Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-Learn
- Streamlit
- Plotly

